Can you add ConnectTimeout configuration to Cassandra config? 

Would work something like this in `cassandraCluster.NewCassandraCluster`
```
	if cfg.ConnectTimeout != "" {
		connectTimeout, err := time.ParseDuration(cfg.ConnectTimeout)
		if err != nil {
			log.Fatalf("Error parsing Cassandra Connect Timeout: %v", err)
		}
		cluster.ConnectTimeout = connectTimeout
	}
```
